name: Food Truck: Fast Street Rush!
description:
Choose your Food Truck and Deliver the Food!

- Many type of Food Trucks to Choose From: Pizza, Burgers, Ice Creams, Hot Dog, Ramen, Sushi...
- Avoid traffic and obstacles and drive the Food Truck as far as you can!
- Upgrade your vehicle to get more power ups and new skins.
- Use the Touch Controls to Avoid the Obstacles

Choose your Food Truck and Play Now!
